data.description: Why live in a condo and pay association fees when you can enjoy the privacy of a single family home at a condo price? Conveniently located near Midway Airport in Clearing. This Ranch style home has 3 bedrooms, 1 bath, washer and dryer and a one car garage.  Large den located at the rear of the property that can be utilized as a multipurpose area. Don't let this opportunity pass you buy. Property will be sold As is.
